high_descs: Go to the desk
Pick up a pencil from the desk
Go to the cabinet with a lamp on top of it
Place the pencil in the top drawer
Turn around and look at the top of the cabinet
Pick up a pencil from the top of the cabinet
Turn around and look back at the cabinet
Place the pencil in the top drawer of the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Place two pencils in a drawer

high_descs: Turn to the left and head to the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Turn right and go to the dresser.
Open the top drawer of the dress, put the pencil inside the drawer and close it.
Turn to the left and then back to the right to face the dresser.
Pick up the pencil off the top of the dresser.
Turn around in a circle and face the dresser.
Put the pencil in the top drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils in the dresser.

high_descs: Turn and go to the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
With the pencil in hand turn and go to the dresser where the lamp is on the right side.
Open the first drawer and place the pencil in the drawer on the right side.
Turn so you are in front of the same dresser but on the left side.
Pick up the pencil that is on the dresser in front of you.
Turn around again so you are now on the right side of the same dresser with the pencil in hand.
Open the drawer and place the pencil on top of the other pencil in there on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils away in the drawer.
